# FavoritesScreen Learning Topics

## High-Level Categories
1. Compose UI Architecture
2. State Management
3. Grid Layout
4. Touch Interactions
5. Theme Support

## Android/Kotlin Concepts Used

### Compose UI
1. Material Components
   - Scaffold
   - TopAppBar
   - LazyVerticalGrid
   - AlertDialog

2. Layout Patterns
   - Box composable
   - Aspect ratio
   - Grid cells
   - Padding

### State Handling
1. Observe State
   - LiveData observation
   - StateFlow collection
   - Remember composables

2. User Interactions
   - Selection management
   - Gesture detection
   - Dialog state

### Navigation
1. Route Management
   - NavController
   - Deep links
   - Back navigation

### Theming
1. Dynamic Theming
   - Dark/Light modes
   - Color schemes
   - Background images

## Key Technologies
- Jetpack Compose
- Material3
- Coil Image Loading
- Navigation Component
- LiveData/StateFlow

